---
import Icon from '../Icon.astro';
---

<section id="projects" class="pt-20 pb-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-background">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6 mb-20">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tighter">
          Selected<br />Projects
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm max-w-xs leading-relaxed">
        Personal builds at the intersection of AI, product thinking, and engineering —
        scoped, designed, and shipped independently.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">

      <!-- Project 1: 7 cols -->
      <div class="md:col-span-7 bg-surface-mid p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-dim flex flex-col justify-between min-h-72">
        <div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary">Gen AI</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider bg-surface-high text-neutral-400">Content Strategy</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-3">LinkedIn Content Generation App</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Generative AI tool to create personalised LinkedIn content, optimising for audience engagement and content relevance. Designed prompt frameworks, content strategies, and iterative testing workflows.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-outline-dim">
          <span class="text-neutral-600 text-xs font-headline uppercase tracking-wider">April 2026</span>
          <Icon name="arrow_outward" size={20} class="text-primary" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Project 2: 5 cols -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 bg-surface-mid p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-dim flex flex-col justify-between min-h-72">
        <div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary">AI Automation</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider bg-surface-high text-neutral-400">Lead Gen</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-3">AI Lead Generation Platform</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">AI-driven platform using Exa APIs to identify high-intent prospects, auto-draft personalised emails, and score leads through intelligent workflow automation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-outline-dim">
          <span class="text-neutral-600 text-xs font-headline uppercase tracking-wider">March 2026</span>
          <Icon name="arrow_outward" size={20} class="text-primary" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Project 3: Full width -->
      <div class="md:col-span-12 bg-surface-mid p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-dim">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
              {['Local LLM','EdTech','Full PRD','Microservices'].map((t, i) => (
                <span class={`px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider ${i === 0 ? 'bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary' : 'bg-surface-high text-neutral-400'}`}>
                  {t}
                </span>
              ))}
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-3">AI-First Learning Management System</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Authored a full PRD covering user personas, system architecture, guardrails, and
              non-functional requirements — then prototyped the system. Features audio interaction
              and voice/text queries for real-time course access. Powered by Qwen 3.5 via Ollama,
              pgvector for retrieval, and containerised microservices.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex md:flex-col gap-4 flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="bg-surface-high px-5 py-4 rounded-lg">
              <div class="font-headline text-base font-bold text-primary">Full PRD</div>
              <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-600 mt-0.5">Spec Coverage</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-high px-5 py-4 rounded-lg">
              <div class="font-headline text-base font-bold text-primary">Privacy-First</div>
              <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-600 mt-0.5">Local LLM</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-outline-dim">
          <span class="text-neutral-600 text-xs font-headline uppercase tracking-wider">February 2026</span>
          <Icon name="arrow_outward" size={20} class="text-primary" />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
